    <custom_item>
      type                 : REGISTRY_SETTING
      description          : "6.8 Set 'Hide Junk Mail UI' to 'Disabled'"
      info                 : "This policy setting controls whether the Junk E-mail Filter is enabled in Outlook. The Junk
