User Configuration\Administrative Templates\Microsoft Outlook 2010\Outlook
Options\Preferences\Junk E-mail\Junk E-mail protection level\Junk E-mail protection
level

Then set the Junk E-mail protection level- Select level- option to High.

Impact-Different users might receive different amounts of junk e-mail. Enabling this setting might
result in setting the junk e-mail protection level too high for some users and too low for
others."
